{
  "id": "2b76f62f-3f7b-42f0-ab2e-b571dabf2ca5",
  "text": "Achieve full autonomous agent capability: discover→plan→execute→verify→submit loop",
  "description": "Build the autonomous discover→plan→execute→verify→submit loop: the agent finds work, plans, executes with real tools, verifies outcomes, and reports — recovering from failures across sessions. IMPORTANT framing: autonomy here is an ENABLER of the Human-AI Cooperation Engine (3d868d5b) — continuity, recovery, and self-improvement so the agent can faithfully carry human-set goals across many sessions — NOT an end in itself. Fully autonomous ASI is a separate moonshot. The agent should default to cooperating with humans (asking where judgment/authorization is needed) rather than maximizing independence.",
